## Idea

A [[polarization]] of a [[symplectic manifold]] induced by a compatible [[KÃ¤hler manifold]] structure.

$$
  \mathcal{P} \subset T_{\mathbb{C}} T X
$$

$$
  \mathcal{P} \cap \overline{\mathcal{P}} = 0
$$

$$
  \mathcal{P} = \left\{J v - i v \;|\; v \in T X \right\}
$$

See also at _[polarization -- KÃ¤hler polarizations](polarization#K%C3%A4hlerPolarization)_ .

